ActYukon Act
SubjectHon. Gregory M. Mulligan - Deputy Judge of the Supreme Court of Yukon ** Appointment **
PrecisOrder (1) appointing the Hon. GREGORY M. MULLIGAN, a former Judge of the Superior Court of Justice of Ontario, to be a DEPUTY JUDGE of the SUPREME COURT OF YUKON; and (2) fixing his remuneration in accordance with the schedule.
